c/cover/l/35/ac/130133_b03fc.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/35/ac/130133_b03fc.jpg"},"summary":"《X战警：进化》动画片于2000年11月在美国WB台首播，2003年10月播完，共4季52集。国内曾由中录华纳于2005年引进发行过第1,2季部分6区DVD和VCD，其译名为《超能战士》。\r\n《X战警：进化》动画由惊奇公司出品，基本忠实于漫画原作。除了X教授和金刚狼等以外主要角色变成青少年。在查尔斯-泽维尔教授的带领下，由变种人(光眼侠,简-格瑞,钢刺,小淘气,夜行者,黑影猫,暴风女,金刚狼)组成的X战警小组为了保卫这个害怕他们的世界而战斗。\r\n在他们成为X战警之前，这些超级英雄都还只是一群平凡的青少年...才怪，这些突变人拥有各式各样的超能力，连一场普通的高中足球赛都可能变成善恶大对决！这群极具天赋的青少年面临的空前的磨难及考验，他们除了要和群体打成一片之外还得忙着拯救世界，且看独眼龙、小淘气、琴葛蕾和其它少年X战警如何面对邪恶势力及校园生活的挑战。","name":"X-Men: Evolution Season 1","name_cn":"X战警：进化 第一季","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Marvel","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫威","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"X战警：进化 第一季"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"超能战士"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"13"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2000年11月4日"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"Kids' WB"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"2001年5月12日"},{"key":"每集时长","value":"22min"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":8,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":3,"7":2,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.6},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":4,"dropped":5,"wish":3,"collect":12,"doing":3},"id":130133,"eps":13,"meta_tags":["TV","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"2000-11-03","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/1e/39/348822_o9Sc5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/1e/39/348822_o9Sc5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/1e/39/348822_o9Sc5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/1e/39/348822_o9Sc5.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/1e/39/348822_o9Sc5.jpg"},"summary":"京都の駅ビルの中にあった手塚治虫ワールド（2011年1月16日閉館）の中に300インチシアターという劇場があり、そこで上映されていたオリジナル短編アニメ。手塚漫画の代表作の、そのエッセンスを詰め込んだアニメーション作品と、京都にまつわる歴史的なエピソードを紹介するアニメーションとの二本立てという形で上映され、その二本を火の鳥がストーリー・テラーとなってつないで行く、という構成です。 「限られた命の中で、愛はどのように不変の力として成長して行くのか」というテーマを、火の鳥は『ブラック・ジャック』のエピソードの中から「おばあちゃん」という物語を選んで紹介します。お金にがめつくて、嫁に対して口を開けば「お金をちょうだい」と小遣いをせびってばかりいる老婆。そんなおばあちゃんに息子夫婦はうんざりしています。家の中はだから口論が耐えず、やすらかな日常は失われているように見えます。ひょんなことからこの一家と知り合ったブラック・ジャックはやがてこのおばあちゃんが瀕死の重病にかかった幼い息子を救うため、大金を要求する名医に治療してもらった過去がある、と知るのです。息子の命を救った医者への治療費を彼女は何十年もかかって払い込み続けているのでした。息子への愛。その代償として、生涯を治療費を払うことだけに費やした老婆。そしてそんな母の思いを知らず、嫁とのいさかいの間に立ってため息をつくだけだった息子。彼が母の真実を知った時、彼はそこに「自分の人生よりも大事な我が子への愛」に生きた母なるものの「愛」を思い知ることになるのです。そして同じだけの愛で母を愛せるのか、とブラック・ジャックは彼に問いかけます。火の鳥はそんな「命よりも大事な愛」こそが永遠の命を持つのだと語り、そしてひとつの都市そのものに永遠の命を与えようとした一大国家プロジェクト『平安遷都』について語っていきます。","name":"ブラック・ジャック / 平安遷都","name_cn":"怪医黑杰克 / 平安迁都","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVA","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"J.C.STAFF","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"森田眞由美","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"经典","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手塚治虫","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1996年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"西田正義","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"怪医黑杰克 / 平安迁都"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Black Jack: Heian Sento"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"2000年11月3日"},{"key":"片长","value":"14分"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://tezukaosamu.net/jp/anime/24.html"},{"key":"话数","value":"2"},{"key":"导演","value":"西田正義"},{"key":"脚本","value":"森田真由美"},{"key":"演出","value":"西田正義"},{"key":"作画监督","value":"西田正義"},{"key":"原画","value":"西田正義"},{"key":"动画检查","value":"岡村隆、田中嘉"},{"key":"美术监督","value":"岡田和夫"},{"key":"色彩设计","value":"宇田川佐東美"},{"key":"录音","value":"スタジオ:タバック"},{"key":"摄影","value":"高橋プロダクション"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":7,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":3,"6":2,"7":2,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":3,"wish":16,"collect":15,"doing":0},"id":348822,"eps":2,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"2000-11-02","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/78/98/110783_ctCT3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/78/98/110783_ctCT3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/78/98/110783_ctCT3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/78/98/110783_ctCT3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/78/98/110783_ctCT3.jpg"},"summary":"The second season of the American animated television series SpongeBob SquarePants, created by Stephen Hillenburg, aired on Nickelodeon from October 26, 2000, to July 26, 2003, and consists of 20 half-hour episodes. The series chronicles the exploits and adventures of the title character and his various friends in the fictional underwater city of Bikini Bottom. The season was executive produced by series creator Hillenburg, who also acted as the showrunner.\r\n\r\nDuring the season's run, SpongeBob SquarePants became Nickelodeon's No. 2 children's program, behind Rugrats. Nearly 40 percent of SpongeBob's audience of 2.2 million were aged 18 to 34. The show signed a marketing deal with Target Corporation and Burger King, expanding its merchandising, and SpongeBob's popularity translated well into sales figures. In 2002, the show was nominated at the Primetime Emmy Awards for Outstanding Children's Program. Tom Kenny and Mary Jo Catlett were individually nominated at the 29th Annie Awards for their voice performances as SpongeBob and Mrs. Puff, respectively. Peter Straus and Paul Tibbitt were also nominated at the ceremony for their work on the \"Christmas Who?\" special. The episodes \"The Secret Box\" and \"Band Geeks\" won at the 2002 Golden Reel Awards for Best Sound Editing in Television—Animation, while the episodes \"Jellyfish Hunter\" and \"The Fry Cook Games\" received a nomination for Best Sound Editing in Television Animation—Music category.\r\n\r\nSeveral compilation DVDs that contained episodes from the season were released. The SpongeBob SquarePants: The Complete 2nd Season DVD was released in Region 1 on October 19, 2004, Region 2 on October 23, 2006, and Region 4 on November 30, 2006.\r\n\r\n简介来自 英文维基百科","name":"SpongeBob SquarePants (Season 2)","name_cn":"海绵宝宝 第二季","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":245,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":228,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":161,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":138,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":87,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":74,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":59,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":57,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动漫世界","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":30,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"一般向","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电视","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV（集数1-49）","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"海绵宝宝","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"经典","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"吐槽","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美漫","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000年11月","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧集","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000-2009","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"没看全","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Nickelodeon_Animation_Studio","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"海绵宝宝 第二季"},{"key":"话数","value":"20"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2000年11月2日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://www.nick.com/shows/spongebob-squarepants"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"Nickelodeon"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"2001年10月12日"},{"key":"导演","value":"Stephen Hillenburg、Paul Tibbitt、Sherm Cohen 等"}],"rating":{"rank":427,"total":890,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":2,"4":2,"5":13,"6":56,"7":251,"8":382,"9":100,"10":83},"score":7.8},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":26,"dropped":25,"wish":57,"collect":2062,"doing":35},"id":110783,"eps":20,"meta_tags":["TV","原创","美国","欧美"],"vo